<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10659901>
    dc:description "FIGS. 303–307. Rhagovelia riu n. sp., structural details; specimens from the Tagula Island. 303. Wingless male, dorsal habitus. 304. Wingless female, dorsal habitus; 303 and 304 from Kolukolu Creek, CL 7194. 305. Male right hind leg, dorsal view; 306. Male left paramere, outer lateral view. 307. Male proctiger, dorsal view; 276–279 from Kalitau Creek, CL 7190." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10659901/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

